{"word":"Caleb","slug":"caleb","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Caleb</b> <a href=\"#/H3612\">H3612</a> <br/> One of the two survivors of the Israelites permitted to enter the land of promise<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=30'>Num 14:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=38'>Num 14:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=65'>Num 26:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=13'>Num 32:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=36'>Deu 1:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=15'>Jos 14:15</a><br/> Sent to Canaan as a spy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=6'>Num 13:6</a><br/> Brings favorable report<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=30'>Num 13:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=9'>Num 14:9</a><br/> Assists in dividing Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=19'>Num 34:19</a><br/> Life of, miraculously saved<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=12'>Num 14:12</a><br/> Leader of the Israelites after Joshua's death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=12'>Jdg 1:12</a><br/> Age of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=10'>Jos 14:10</a><br/> Inheritance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=15'>Jos 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=16'>Jos 15:16</a><br/> Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=15'>1Ch 4:15</a>"}]}